Filesystem generation and setup:

Method 1: Using busybox generated fs and partitioned sd card
-refer to BBB fs instructions

Method 2: Buildroot settings

-do defconfig for pi3, go to menu and filesystem images
-ext4 root fs, and ext 4 variant
-exact size:
-tar the rootfs, compression method gzip

-Filesystem & flash utilities
-dofstools and e2fsprogs>fsck, resize2fs, e2image

-in Target Packages>System tools:
-enable util-linux->libblkid, libmount, libuuid, libfdisk

-in Target Packages>Shell & Utilities
-enable sudo
